    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is almost cooked, add the <strong>mangetout</strong> to the pan and cook for 3-4 min further or until tender with a bite</p><p>Meanwhile, cut the <strong>red</strong> <strong>chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p><p>Chop the <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
